title: Printer's Sample Book (USA), 1882
creditline: Gift of Frederick J. Whitehead from the collection compiled by his father Cornelius Whitehead at the Pacific Print Works of Lawrence, Massachusetts
description: Small notebook with handwritten formulas for dyestuffs to be used on printed textiles. Contains 78 samples of printed fabrics.

tombstone.epitaph: Printer's Sample Book (USA), 1882; Manufactured by Old Pacific Print Works ; paper and cotton; Gift of Frederick J. Whitehead from the collection compiled by his father Cornelius Whitehead at the Pacific Print Works of Lawrence, Massachusetts; 1945-55-30
